OL,6,FA Sinn Fein motion on unaffordable
OL,7,Fchildcare is to be debated in Stormont
OL,8,Fon Monday.
OL,10,FThe motion is expected to highlight
OL,11,Fthe lack of affordable childcare and
OL,12,Fthe need for greater investment in the
OL,13,Fsector.
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland is the only part of
OL,16,Fthe UK with no free childcare
OL,17,Fprovision and no formal childcare
OL,18,Fstrategy.
