OL,3,CAffordable childcare costs under
OL,4,Cspotlight
OL,6,FThe manager of one local nursery says
OL,7,Fsome parents have been forced out of
OL,8,Fwork as they are unable to meet
OL,9,Fchildcare costs.
OL,11,FIn England, parents benefit from
OL,12,Fchildcare support measures which were
OL,13,Fexpanded in March last year to include
OL,14,F30 hours of free provision for
OL,15,Fchildren under 5 from September 2025.
OL,17,FIn Northern Ireland four and five year
OL,18,Folds here receive 12.5 hours of free
OL,19,Fpre-school classes but childcare is
OL,20,Fnot funded.
