OL,4,Cspotlight
OL,6,FThe newly formed Executive must now
OL,7,Fdecide how much money goes into
OL,8,Fproviding support for parents at a
OL,9,Ftime when departments are struggling
OL,10,Fwith increasing demands and budgetary
OL,11,Fconstraints.
OL,13,FThe issue of childcare has attracted
OL,14,Fcross-party support.
OL,16,FAlliance MLA and childcare
OL,17,Fspokesperson Kate Nicholl has called
OL,18,Fon the Minister of Education to
OL,19,Furgently bring forward a plan for
OL,20,Fdelivering childcare reform.
