OL,4,Cspotlight
OL,6,FThe South Belfast representative said:
OL,7,F"It is simply unacceptable that
OL,8,Fchildcare providers are being forced
OL,9,Fto make decisions between raising fees
OL,10,Ffor parents, reducing days, or in some
OL,11,Fcases, closing altogether.
OL,13,F"With the Assembly and Executive now
OL,14,Frestored, it is clear that there is a
OL,15,Fcross-party shared ambition to deliver
OL,16,Fon childcare reform.
OL,18,F"With day one now come and gone, we
OL,19,Fmust move towards delivering on the
OL,20,Fcommitments made."
