OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the affordable
OL,7,Fchildcare debate, Sharon Malcolm the
OL,8,Fmanager of the Belfast nursery
OL,9,FPuddleducks said: "The return of the
OL,10,FAssembly now allows for vital issues
OL,11,Fsuch as the challenges around
OL,12,Fchildcare provision to be highlighted
OL,13,Fwith focus and much greater attention
OL,14,Fto actual solutions."
OL,16,F"This is a critical priority not just
OL,17,Ffor parents by ensuring that families
OL,18,Fcan meet the costs of childcare, but
OL,19,Ffor the wider economy as well."
